msgstr ""
"hierdie is die skrif tipe gebruik word aan vertoon teks in konqueror "
"vensters."

#: fontopts.cpp:90
msgid "This is the font size used to display text in Konqueror windows."
msgstr ""
"hierdie is die skrif tipe grootte gebruik word aan vertoon teks in konqueror "
"vensters."

#: fontopts.cpp:96
msgid "Normal Text Color:"
msgstr "normale teks kleur:"

#: fontopts.cpp:102
msgid "This is the color used to display text in Konqueror windows."
msgstr "hierdie is die kleur gebruik word aan vertoon teks in konqueror vensters."

#: fontopts.cpp:129
msgid "&Text Background Color:"
msgstr "teks agtergrond kleur:"

#: fontopts.cpp:137
msgid "This is the color used behind the text for the icons on the desktop."
msgstr ""
"hierdie is die kleur gebruik word agter die teks vir die ikoone op die "
"werkskerm."

#: fontopts.cpp:148
msgid "&Word-wrap icon text"
msgstr "Word-wrap ikoon teks"

#: fontopts.cpp:152
msgid ""
"Checking this option will wrap long filenames to multiple lines, rather than "
"showing only the part of the filename that fits on a single line.<p> Hint: "
"if you uncheck this option, you can still see the word-wrapped filename by "
"pausing the mouse pointer over the icon."
msgstr ""
"toetsing hierdie opsie sal oorvloei lang lêername aan veelvuldige lyne, "
"eerder as te wys slegs die deel van die lêernaam wat pas op 'n enkel "
"lyn.<p> leidraad: as jy ontkies hierdie opsie, jy kan nogsteeds sien die "
"word-wrapped lêernaam deur pouseer die muis wyser bo die ikoon."

#: fontopts.cpp:161
msgid "&Underline filenames"
msgstr "onderstreep lêername"

#: fontopts.cpp:165
msgid ""
"Checking this option will result in filenames being underlined, so that they "
"look like links on a web page. Note: to complete the analogy, make sure that "
"single click activation is enabled in the mouse control module."
msgstr ""
"toetsing hierdie opsie sal resultaat in lêername te wees geonderstreep, "
"sodat wat hulle kyk hou van skakel op 'n web bladsy. nota: aan volledige die "
"analogie, maak seker wat enkel kliek aktivering is geaktiveer in die muis "
"kontrole module."

#: fontopts.cpp:174
msgid "Display filesizes in b&ytes"
msgstr "vertoon lêer groottes in grepe"

#: fontopts.cpp:178
msgid ""
"Checking this option will result in filesizes being displayed in bytes. "
"Otherwise filesizes are converted to kilobytes or megabytes if appropriate."
msgstr ""
"toetsing hierdie opsie sal resultaat in lêer groottes te wees vertoon in "
"grepe. andersins lêer groottes word omgeskakel aan kilogrepe of megagrepe "
"as geskikte."

