#: main.cpp:114
msgid ""
"<h1>File Manager</h1> In this module, you can configure various aspects of "
"Konqueror's file manager functionality. Please note that the Konqueror's web "
"browser functionality has its own configuration module.<p>"
" The configuration options for the file manager are organized under four "
"tabs as described below: <h2>Behavior</h2> This tab contains global options "
"for Konqueror, such as the directory tree's reaction to changes in adjoining "
"views, whether directories are opened in new windows, etc. "
"<h2>Appearance</h2> This tab contains options customizing the appearance of "
"Konqueror windows, such as the font and color of text, background color, "
"etc. <h2>Trash</h2> This tab contains options for customizing the behavior "
"of Konqueror when you \"delete\" a file."
msgstr ""
"<h1>lêer bestuurder</h1> in hierdie module, jy kan konfigureer verskeie "
"aspekte van konqueror se lêer bestuurder funksionaliteit. asseblief nota "
"wat die konqueror se web blaaier funksionaliteit het its eie opstelling "
"module.<p>"
" die opstelling opsies vir die lêer bestuurder word georganiseerd onder "
"vier oortjies as beskryf onder: <h2>gedrag</h2> hierdie oortjie bevat "
"globale opsies vir konqueror, soos as die gids boom se reaksie aan verander "
"in aangrensende aansigte, hetsy gidse word geöpende in nuwe vensters, etc. "
"<h2>voorkoms</h2> hierdie oortjie bevat opsies pasmaking die voorkoms van "
"konqueror vensters, soos as die skrif tipe en kleur van teks, agtergrond "
"kleur, etc. <h2>gemors</h2> hierdie oortjie bevat opsies vir pasmaking die "
"gedrag van konqueror wanneer jy \"uitvee\" 'n lêer."

#: main.cpp:154
msgid "&Desktop"
msgstr "werkskerm"

#: main.cpp:162
msgid "&Number of Desktops"
msgstr "nommer van werkskerms"

#: main.cpp:218 rootopts.cpp:584
msgid ""
"<h1>Desktop</h1>\n"
"This module allows you to choose various options\n"
"for your desktop, including the way in which icons are arranged, the\n"
"location of your desktop directory, and the pop-up menus associated\n"
"with clicks of the middle and right mouse buttons on the desktop.\n"
"Use the \"Whats This?\" (Shift+F1) to get help on specific options."
msgstr ""
"<h1>werkskerm</h1>\n"
"hierdie module laat toe jy aan kies verskeie opsies\n"
"vir jou werkskerm, insluitend die weg in wat ikoone word gerangskik, die\n"
"ligging van jou werkskerm gids, en die pop-up kieslyste geassosieer\n"
"met klieke van die middelste en regterkant muis knoppies op die werkskerm.\n"
"gebruik die \"Whats hierdie?\" (verskuiwende+f1) aan kry hulp op spesifieke "
"opsies."

#: rootopts.cpp:65
msgid "Sound Files"
msgstr "klank lêers"

#: rootopts.cpp:107
msgid "Align Icons &Vertically on Desktop"
msgstr "oplyn ikoone vertikaal op werkskerm"

#: rootopts.cpp:110
msgid ""
"Check this option if you want the icons on the desktop to be aligned "
"vertically (in columns). If you leave this option unchecked, desktop icons "
"are aligned horizontally.<p> Note that you can drag icons wherever you want "
"to on the desktop. When you choose \"Arrange Icons\" from the Desktop menu, "
"icons will be arranged horizontally or vertically."
msgstr ""
"bevestig hierdie opsie as jy wil hê die ikoone op die werkskerm aan wees "
"opgelyn vertikaal (in kolomme). as jy los hierdie opsie onbevestig, "
"werkskerm ikoone word opgelyn horisontaal.<p> nota wat jy kan trek ikoone "
"waar ook al jy wil hê aan op die werkskerm. wanneer jy kies \"rangskik "
"ikoone\" van die werkskerm kieslys, ikoone sal wees gerangskik horisontaal "
"of vertikaal."

#: rootopts.cpp:118
msgid "Show &Hidden Files on Desktop"
msgstr "vertoon weg gesteekte lêers op werkskerm"

#: rootopts.cpp:121
msgid ""
"If you check this option, any files in your desktop directory that begin "
"with a period (.) will be shown. Usually, such files contain configuration "
"information, and remain hidden from view.<p> For example, files which are "
"named \".directory\" are plain text files which contain information for "
"Konqueror, such as the icon to use in displaying a directory, the order in "
"which files should be sorted, etc. You should not change or delete these "
"files unless you know what you are doing!"
msgstr ""
"as jy bevestig hierdie opsie, enige lêers in jou werkskerm gids wat begin "
"met 'n periode (.) sal wees vertoon. gewoonlik, soos lêers bevat opstelling "
"informasie, en bly weg gesteekte van besigtig.<p> vir voorbeeld, lêers wat "
"word genaamd \".gids\" word eenvoudig teks lêers wat bevat informasie vir "
"konqueror, soos as die ikoon aan gebruik in vertooning 'n gids, die volgorde "
"in wat lêers moet wees gesorteer, etc. jy moet nie verander of uitvee "
"hierdie lêers tensy jy ken wat jy word doen!"

#: rootopts.cpp:132
msgid "Enable Desktop &Menu"
msgstr "aktiveer werkskerm kieslys"

#: rootopts.cpp:135
msgid ""
"Check this option if you want the desktop popup menus to appear on the top "
"of the screen in the style of Macintosh.  This setting is independent of the "
"global top-level menu setting that applies to KDE applications."
msgstr ""
"bevestig hierdie opsie as jy wil hê die werkskerm opspring kieslyste aan "
"verskyn op die bo van die skerm in die styl van macintosh.  hierdie opset is "
"onafhanklike van die globale bo-level kieslys opset wat van toepassing is "
"aan kde programme."

#: rootopts.cpp:141
msgid "Support Programs in Desktop Window"
msgstr "ondersteun programme in werkskerm venster"

#: rootopts.cpp:144
msgid ""
"Check this option if you want to run X11 programs that draw into the desktop "
"such as xsnow, xpenguin or xmountain. If you have problems with applications "
"like netscape that check the root window for running instances, disable this "
"option."
msgstr ""
"bevestig hierdie opsie as jy wil hê aan hardloop x11 programme wat teken "
"binnein die werkskerm soos as xsneeu, xpikkewyn of xberg. as jy het probleme "
"met programme hou van netscape wat bevestig die root venster vir wat loop "
"instansies, deaktiveer hierdie opsie."

#: rootopts.cpp:152
msgid "Show Previews for:"
msgstr "vertoon voorskoue vir:"

#: rootopts.cpp:154
msgid "Select for which types of files you want to enable preview images"
msgstr "kies vir wat tipes van lêers jy wil hê aan aktiveer voorskou beelde"

#: rootopts.cpp:162
msgid "Clicks on the desktop"
msgstr "klieke op die werkskerm"

#: rootopts.cpp:165
msgid "Left Button"
msgstr "links knoppie"

#: rootopts.cpp:166
msgid ""
"You can choose what happens when you click the left button of your pointing "
"device on the desktop:"
msgstr ""
"jy kan kies wat gebeur wanneer jy kliek die links knoppie van jou aanwys "
"toestel op die werkskerm:"

#: rootopts.cpp:169
msgid "Right Button"
msgstr "regterkant knoppie"

#: rootopts.cpp:170
msgid ""
"You can choose what happens when you click the right button of your pointing "
"device on the desktop:"
msgstr ""
"jy kan kies wat gebeur wanneer jy kliek die regterkant knoppie van jou "
"aanwys toestel op die werkskerm:"

#: rootopts.cpp:188 rootopts.cpp:239
msgid ""
" <ul><li><em>No action:</em> as you might guess, nothing happens!</li> "
"<li><em>Window list menu:</em> a menu showing all windows on all virtual "
"desktops pops up. You can click on the desktop name to switch to that "
"desktop, or on a window name to shift focus to that window, switching "
"desktops if necessary, and restoring the window if it is hidden. Hidden or "
"minimized windows are represented with their names in parentheses.</li> "
"<li><em>Desktop menu:</em> a context menu for the desktop pops up. Among "
"other things, this menu has options for configuring the display, locking the "
"screen, and logging out of KDE.</li> <li><em>Application menu:</em> the "
"\"K\" menu pops up. This might be useful for quickly accessing applications "
"if you like to keep the panel (also known as \"Kicker\") hidden from "
"view.</li></ul>"
msgstr ""
" <ul><li><em>nee aksie:</em> as jy dalk skat, niks gebeur!</li> "
"<li><em>venster lys kieslys:</em> 'n kieslys te wys alle vensters op alle "
"virtuele werkskerms spring begin. jy kan kliek op die werkskerm naam aan "
"wissel aan wat werkskerm, van op 'n venster naam aan verskuiwende fokus aan "
"wat venster, omskakeling werkskerms as nodige, en herstel die venster as dit "
"is weg gesteekte. weg gesteekte van geminimeer vensters word verteenwoordig "
"met hulle name in aanhalingstekens.</li> <li><em>werkskerm kieslys:</em> 'n "
"konteks kieslys vir die werkskerm spring begin. onder ander dinge, hierdie "
"kieslys het opsies vir konfigurering van die vertoon, sluit van die skerm, "
"en afteken uit van kde.</li> <li><em>aansoek kieslys:</em>"
" die \"k\" kieslys spring begin. hierdie dalk wees bruikbare vir vinnig "
"toegang te kry tot programme as jy hou van aan hou die paneel (asook bekend "
"as \"kicker\") weg gesteekte van besigtig.</li></ul>"

#: rootopts.cpp:205
msgid "Middle button"
msgstr "middelste knoppie"

#: rootopts.cpp:212
msgid ""
"You can choose what happens when you click the middle button of your "
"pointing device on the desktop: <ul><li><em>No action:</em> as you might "
"guess, nothing happens!</li> <li><em>Window list menu:</em> a menu showing "
"all windows on all virtual desktops pops up. You can click on the desktop "
"name to switch to that desktop, or on a window name to shift focus to that "
"window, switching desktops if necessary, and restoring the window if it is "
"hidden. Hidden or minimized windows are represented with their names in "
"parentheses.</li> <li><em>Desktop menu:</em> a context menu for the desktop "
"pops up. Among other things, this menu has options for configuring the "
"display, locking the screen, and logging out of KDE.</li> "
"<li><em>Application menu:</em> the \"K\" menu pops up. This might be useful "
"for quickly accessing applications if you like to keep the panel (also known "
"as \"Kicker\") hidden from view.</li></ul>"
msgstr ""
"jy kan kies wat gebeur wanneer jy kliek die middelste knoppie van jou aanwys "
"toestel op die werkskerm: <ul><li><em>nee aksie:</em> as jy dalk skat, niks "
"gebeur!</li> <li><em>venster lys kieslys:</em> 'n kieslys te wys alle "
"vensters op alle virtuele werkskerms spring begin. jy kan kliek op die "
"werkskerm naam aan wissel aan wat werkskerm, van op 'n venster naam aan "
"verskuiwende fokus aan wat venster, omskakeling werkskerms as nodige, en "
"herstel die venster as dit is weg gesteekte. weg gesteekte van geminimeer "
"vensters word verteenwoordig met hulle name in aanhalingstekens.</li> "
"<li><em>werkskerm kieslys:</em> 'n konteks kieslys vir die werkskerm spring "
"begin. onder ander dinge, hierdie kieslys het opsies vir konfigurering van "
"die vertoon, sluit van die skerm, en afteken uit van kde.</li> "
"<li><em>aansoek kieslys:</em> die \"k\" kieslys spring begin. hierdie dalk "
"wees bruikbare vir vinnig toegang te kry tot programme as jy hou van aan hou "
"die paneel (asook bekend as \"kicker\") weg gesteekte van besigtig.</li></ul>"

#: rootopts.cpp:262
msgid "Desktop &path:"
msgstr "werkskerm gids soeklys:"

#: rootopts.cpp:268
msgid ""
"This directory contains all the files which you see on your desktop. You can "
"change the location of this directory if you want to, and the contents will "
"move automatically to the new location as well."
msgstr ""
"hierdie gids bevat alle die lêers wat jy sien op jou werkskerm. jy kan "
"verander die ligging van hierdie gids as jy wil hê aan, en die inhoud sal "
"beweeg automaties aan die nuwe ligging as goed."

#: rootopts.cpp:274
msgid "&Trash path:"
msgstr "gemors gids soeklys:"

#: rootopts.cpp:280
msgid ""
"This directory contains deleted files (until you empty the trashcan). You "
"can change the location of this directory if you want to, and the contents "
"will move automatically to the new location as well."
msgstr ""
"hierdie gids bevat uitgevee lêers (totdat jy leeg die asblik). jy kan "
"verander die ligging van hierdie gids as jy wil hê aan, en die inhoud sal "
"beweeg automaties aan die nuwe ligging as goed."

#: rootopts.cpp:288
msgid "&Autostart path:"
msgstr "outomatiese begin gids soeklys:"

#: rootopts.cpp:294
msgid ""
"This directory contains applications or links to applications (shortcuts) "
"that you want to have started automatically whenever KDE starts. You can "
"change the location of this directory if you want to, and the contents will "
"move automatically to the new location as well."
msgstr ""
"hierdie gids bevat programme van skakel aan programme (kortpaaie) wat jy wil "
"hê aan het beginne automaties wanneer ook al kde beginne. jy kan verander "
"die ligging van hierdie gids as jy wil hê aan, en die inhoud sal beweeg "
"automaties aan die nuwe ligging as goed."

#: rootopts.cpp:303
msgid "&Documents path:"
msgstr "dokumente gids soeklys:"

